prompts.frontCover:
A vibrant, flat 2D comic book style birthday card front. In the center, a superhero-themed illustration of two specific people.

Person 1 (Lao Lao): A young East Asian woman (20-25) with long, straight, side-parted dark brown hair and thin, round metal-framed glasses. She is positioned slightly left of center, illustrated in a dynamic superhero pose with a warm, happy smile and arms crossed confidently. She wears a light blue crewneck sweatshirt with a circular "ROCKY MO...IDGE" logo and black pants.

Person 2 (Jordan): Standing slightly behind her, a young Southeast Asian or East Asian man (20-25) with short, textured black hair. He's illustrated as her trusty sidekick, in a tan hoodie and dark maroon sweatpants with a white side stripe, striking a supportive pose with a wide, cheerful smile.

The background is a classic comic book action scene with a bright yellow sunburst explosion, halftone dot patterns, and action lines radiating from the center. A large, stylized speech bubble emerges from near the couple.

Centered within the speech bubble, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text:
"Happy Birthday to our favorite superhero, Lao Lao!"

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
